(Corrects spelling of chairman’s surname.)  AVI Ltd. (AVI)  said Angus Band will retire
as chairman on Nov. 2 and the company has appointed Gavin Tipper
as his successor.  Tipper starts on July 1 to “ensure an orderly
transition,” it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
